note:
I’m 65 and I still don’t know what I want to be when I grow up. My maturity level is about half my age. I’ve been a Liberal resister since I was 17. I’m still as passionate and informed but I’m running on fumes.

My timeline will be full of things that bring me joy or a chuckle.

My editors are Shiloh, a Samoyed, and Noel, a Cavalier King Charles Spaniel. None of us can spell.
